comment: Butler (CHI) has established position and is firming up when he takes the contact from Bjelica (MIN).
Gasol (CHI) and Wiggins (MIN) make incidental foot to foot contact that causes Wiggins to briefly lose his balance.
LHH shows Towns (MIN) makes contact with Butler's (CHI) arm that affects his layup attempt.
Gibson (CHI) makes incidental contact with Wiggins' (MIN) arm that does not affect his dunk attempt.
Wiggins (MIN) maintains legal guarding position and jumps vertically as he defends Butler's (CHI) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Bjelica (MIN) makes incidental contact with Gasol (CHI) during the rebound attempt.
Wiggins (MIN) fumbles the ball while starting his upward motion. He may be the first to touch the ball after fumbling.
Bjelica (MIN) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Mirotic's (CHI) shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) makes contact with the ball before it has reached its apex and is still on its upward flight toward the basket.
Gasol (CHI) makes contact with Rubio's (MIN) body and arm that affects his drive to the basket and layup attempt.
LHH shows Butler (CHI) hook Wiggins (MIN) as he drives into the paint.
Mirotic (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Towns' (MIN) shot attempt.
Rose (CHI) makes contact with the ball as he reaches in to defend Wiggins' (MIN) shot attempt.
Gibson (CHI) does not clamp Wiggins (MIN) as he gathers the offensive rebound.
Towns (MIN) does not dislodge Gasol (CHI) during rebounding.
McDermott (CHI) makes contact with Prince's (MIN) body that affects his layup attempt.
[Observable in production angle] LHH and L-Slash show McDermott's (CHI) heel touch the line before he attempts his shot.
Prince (MIN) cleanly blocks McDermott's (CHI) jump shot.
Gasol (CHI) commits a take foul on Bjelica (MIN).
